query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it3.info in ('pictorial','LD video quality','runtimes','taglines','sound mix','mpaa','plot','LD laserdisc title','color info','certificates','agent address','LD disc format','quotes','keywords','LD frequency response','languages','LD color information','height','trivia') AND cct2.kind in ('cast','complete+verified','crew') AND t.production_year > 1990 AND rt.role not like '%Tristan Cowen%' AND rt.role not like '%Katy Monahan Huntley%' AND rt.role not like '%Samson Yee%' AND (mc.note like '%Portugal%' OR mc.note like '%Italy%' OR mc.note like '%India%') AND k.keyword not like '%comedy%' AND k.keyword not like '%escape%' AND k.keyword not like '%treasure%' AND k.keyword not like '%survival%' AND k.keyword not like '%dream%' AND (chn.name like '%Tony Stark%')
